<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CSS Concepts - Interactive Guide</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .concept {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #764ba2;
        }
        
        .concept h3 {
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .concept p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .demo-box {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border: 2px dashed #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        code {
            background: #2d2d2d;
            color: #f8f8f2;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        /* Box Model Examples */
        .box-model-demo {
            width: 300px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 5px solid #667eea;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #ffd700;
        }
        
        .box-sizing-normal {
            box-sizing: content-box;
            width: 200px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 5px solid red;
            background: #ffcccb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .box-sizing-border {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            width: 200px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 5px solid green;
            background: #90ee90;
        }
        
        /* Font Examples */
        .font-demo-1 {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        
        .font-demo-2 {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        
        .text-demo-1 {
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .text-demo-2 {
            text-align: right;
            text-transform: capitalize;
            line-height: 2;
        }
        
        /* Background Examples */
        .bg-demo-1 {
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        
        .bg-demo-2 {
            background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #333;
        }
        
        /* Display Examples */
        .display-block {
            display: block;
            background: #ffcccb;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .display-inline {
            display: inline;
            background: #90ee90;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        
        .display-inline-block {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #add8e6;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        
        .display-none {
            display: none;
        }
        
        .visibility-hidden {
            visibility: hidden;
        }
        
        .opacity-demo {
            opacity: 0.5;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .overflow-demo {
            width: 300px;
            height: 100px;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            overflow: scroll;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üé® CSS Concepts - Visual Learning Guide</h1>
        
        <!-- Box Model Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>üì¶ 4. Box Model</h2>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Box Model Kya Hai?</h3>
                <p>Har HTML element ek box ki tarah hota hai jisme 4 parts hote hain:</p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li><strong>Content:</strong> Actual content (text, image)</li>
                    <li><strong>Padding:</strong> Content ke around space (andar ki taraf)</li>
                    <li><strong>Border:</strong> Padding ke around boundary line</li>
                    <li><strong>Margin:</strong> Border ke bahar space (dusre elements se distance)</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="box-model-demo">
                        Content Area<br>
                        Padding: 20px<br>
                        Border: 5px solid blue<br>
                        Margin: 20px
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>box-sizing: border-box</h3>
                <p><code>box-sizing: content-box</code> (default): Width sirf content ki hoti hai</p>
                <p><code>box-sizing: border-box</code>: Width mein padding aur border bhi include hote hain</p>
                
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="box-sizing-normal">
                        content-box<br>
                        Total width = 250px<br>
                        (200 + 20*2 + 5*2)
                    </div>
                    <div class="box-sizing-border">
                        border-box<br>
                        Total width = 200px<br>
                        (padding+border included)
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Text & Font Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>‚úçÔ∏è 5. Text & Font Styling</h2>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Font Properties</h3>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="font-demo-1">
                        <code>font-family: Arial</code><br>
                        <code>font-size: 18px</code><br>
                        <code>font-weight: normal</code><br>
                        Yeh normal text hai with Arial font
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="font-demo-2">
                        <code>font-family: Courier New</code><br>
                        <code>font-size: 24px</code><br>
                        <code>font-weight: bold</code><br>
                        <code>letter-spacing: 3px</code><br>
                        Bold Text with Letter Spacing
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Text Styling</h3>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="text-demo-1">
                        text-align: center<br>
                        text-transform: uppercase<br>
                        text-decoration: underline
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="text-demo-2">
                        text-align: right<br>
                        text-transform: capitalize<br>
                        line-height: 2 (double spacing)<br>
                        Yeh line double height ke saath hai
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Background & Border Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>üé® 6. Background & Border</h2>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Background Properties</h3>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="bg-demo-1">
                        <code>background-color: #667eea</code><br>
                        <code>border-radius: 10px</code><br>
                        Simple solid color background
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="bg-demo-2">
                        <code>background-image: gradient</code><br>
                        <code>border: 3px solid #333</code><br>
                        <code>border-radius: 20px</code><br>
                        Gradient background with border
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Display Section -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>üëÅÔ∏è 7. Display, Visibility & Overflow</h2>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Display Property</h3>
                <p><strong>display: block</strong> - Full width leta hai, naye line pe start hota hai</p>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="display-block">Block Element 1</div>
                    <div class="display-block">Block Element 2</div>
                </div>
                
                <p><strong>display: inline</strong> - Sirf content jitna width, same line pe rahta hai</p>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <span class="display-inline">Inline 1</span>
                    <span class="display-inline">Inline 2</span>
                    <span class="display-inline">Inline 3</span>
                </div>
                
                <p><strong>display: inline-block</strong> - Inline ki tarah same line pe, but width/height set kar sakte hain</p>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="display-inline-block">Box 1</div>
                    <div class="display-inline-block">Box 2</div>
                    <div class="display-inline-block">Box 3</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Visibility & Opacity</h3>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <p><code>opacity: 0.5</code> - 50% transparent</p>
                    <div class="opacity-demo">
                        Main 50% transparent hun but jagah leta hun
                    </div>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><code>visibility: hidden</code> - Dikhta nahi but jagah leta hai</p>
                    <div>Pehla box</div>
                    <div class="visibility-hidden">Main hidden hun (jagah occupied hai)</div>
                    <div>Teesra box</div>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><code>display: none</code> - Na dikhta hai, na jagah leta hai</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="concept">
                <h3>Overflow Property</h3>
                <p>Jab content box se bada ho jaye:</p>
                <div class="demo-box">
                    <div class="overflow-demo">
                        <code>overflow: scroll</code><br><br>
                        Yeh bahut lamba content hai jo box se bahar ja raha hai.
                        Isiliye scroll bars aa gaye hain. Tum scroll kar ke pura content 
                        padh sakte ho. Overflow property control karta hai ki extra content 
                        ka kya karna hai. Options hain: hidden (chupa do), scroll (scrollbar do),
                        auto (zarurat hone pe scrollbar do), visible (overflow hone do).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Instructions -->
        <div class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white;">
            <h2 style="color: white; border-bottom-color: white;">üìö Instructions</h2>
            <ul style="line-height: 2; margin-left: 20px;">
                <li>Har section mein live examples diye gaye hain</li>
                <li>Code snippets <code>dark background</code> mein likhe hain</li>
                <li>Visual demos colored boxes mein hain</li>
                <li>Browser DevTools (F12) open karke inspect karo</li>
                <li>Values change karke experiment karo</li>
                <li>Har property ka effect seedha dikh jayega</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>